<section class="hero">
    <p class="hero-kicker">Czech E-Commerce Platform</p>
    <h1>Modern gun store stack on .NET 8, MVC, Identity and PostgreSQL.</h1>
    <p>
        This baseline is now ready for the bachelor thesis flow: authentication, role-based access,
        product listing and protected admin management.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn-modern" asp-controller="Weapons" asp-action="Index">Browse products</a>
        @if (User.IsInRole("Admin"))
        {
            <a class="btn-soft" asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="Orders" asp-action="Index">Open approvals</a>
        }
        else
        {
            <a class="btn-soft" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">Create account</a>
        }
    </div>
</section>

<section class="feature-grid">
    <article class="feature-card">
        <h3>Security baseline</h3>
        <p>Identity authentication, role checks and anti-forgery protection on all write operations.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
        <h3>Layered backend</h3>
        <p>Web uses Application services, while data access stays in Infrastructure through EF Core.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature-card">
        <h3>PostgreSQL runtime</h3>
        <p>Dockerized database with migrations ready for repeatable local development.</p>
    </article>
</section>
